ling narratives that captivate audiences and drive business growth. Over the span of her experience, she has shown her expertise in writing through blogs, PRs, datasheets, white papers, social media marketing, case studies, technical articles, and so on.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https:\\\/\\\/www.linkedin.com\\\/in\\\/krishnanjali-ku-9b2141185\"],\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/author\\\/krishnanjali\"}]}<\/script>\n<!-- \/ Yoast SEO plugin. -->","yoast_head_json":{"title":"Why the Humanities Are More Important Than Ever in the Age of AI\u00a0 - Online Manipal","description":"Why humanities matter more than ever in the age of AI. Explore how critical thinking, ethics, and cultural understanding shape better decisions in a tech-driven world.","robots":{"index":"index","follow":"follow","max-snippet":"max-snippet:-1","max-image-preview":"max-image-preview:large","max-video-preview":"max-video-preview:-1"},"canonical":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/29476737","og_locale":"en_GB","og_type":"article","og_title":"Why the Humanities Are More Important Than Ever in the Age of AI\u00a0 - Online Manipal","og_description":"Why humanities matter more than ever in the age of AI. Explore how critical thinking, ethics, and cultural understanding shape better decisions in a tech-driven world.","og_url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai","og_site_name":"Online Manipal","article_publisher":"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal","article_published_time":"2026-05-05T04:19:50+00:00","og_image":[{"width":2400,"height":794,"url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/05\/Why-the-Humanities-Are-More-Important-Than-Ever-in-the-Age-of-AI@2x.png","type":"image\/png"}],"author":"Krishnanjali KU","twitter_card":"summary_large_image","twitter_misc":{"Written by":"Krishnanjali KU","Estimated reading time":"5 minutes"},"schema":{"@context":"https:\/\/schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai","url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai","name":"Why the Humanities Are More Important Than Ever in the Age of AI\u00a0 - Online Manipal","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai#primaryimage"},"image":{"@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai#primaryimage"},"thumbnailUrl":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/05\/Why-the-Humanities-Are-More-Important-Than-Ever-in-the-Age-of-AI@2x.png","datePublished":"2026-05-05T04:19:50+00:00","description":"Why humanities matter more than ever in the age of AI. Explore how critical thinking, ethics, and cultural understanding shape better decisions in a tech-driven world.","breadcrumb":{"@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai#breadcrumb"},"inLanguage":"en-GB","potentialAction":[{"@type":"ReadAction","target":["https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai"]}]},{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-GB","@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai#primaryimage","url":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/05\/Why-the-Humanities-Are-More-Important-Than-Ever-in-the-Age-of-AI@2x.png","contentUrl":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/05\/Why-the-Humanities-Are-More-Important-Than-Ever-in-the-Age-of-AI@2x.png","width":2400,"height":794},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","@id":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/humanities-importance-in-age-of-ai#breadcrumb","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https:\/\/www.onli